This is a University Intellectual Property Office (UCC IPO) management system built with:
- React 18 + TypeScript + Vite
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- Supabase (PostgreSQL) for database and auth
- Supabase Edge Functions for server-side logic
- React Router v7 for navigation
- Lucide React for icons

The Supabase project ID is: mqfftubqlwiemtxpagps

Key architectural decisions:
- All database operations use Supabase client (@supabase/supabase-js)
- Authentication is handled via Supabase Auth with email/password
- RLS (Row Level Security) is enforced on all tables
- Edge Functions handle sensitive operations (user registration, email sending, PDF generation)
- The users table uses auth_user_id (not id) to map to Supabase auth UIDs

Do not install additional npm packages unless absolutely necessary.
Do not use purple, indigo, or violet color schemes.
Always maintain RLS policies when modifying database schema.
